verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Lord, speak to me, that I may speak
In the living echoes of Thy tone;
As Thou hast sought, so let me seek Thine
Erring children lost and lone.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}O teach me, Lord, that I may teach
The precious things Thou dost impart;
And wing my words that they may reach
The hidden depths of many a heart.{/lang-eng}
